desks.Body:
The Dart NE02 sit-stand electric height adjustable desk is finished in a white ash coloured melamine, with a white powder coated frame.

This single motor desk is designed to fit into your stylish office decor, while providing easy to use ergonomic function. The Dart NE02 is equipped with a load capacity of 70kg and will easily carry monitors, CPUs, and any other accessories required for your workspace.

The desk adjusts with built in controls, at a speed of 25mm/sec, which is fast enough to keep your work momentum going while keeping you energised by alternating your work position, with the addition of four memory settings for quick adjustments. The Dart has a very low power consumption and for safety includes an anti-collision sensor to ensure the desk won't pinch or trap surrounding items.

Easy to assemble, easy to keep clean, safe, and ergonomic, the Dart NE02 is an investment in your workspace and your efficiency.

The desk adjusts with built in controls, at a speed of 25mm/sec, which is fast enough to keep your work momentum going while keeping you energised by alternating your work position. 

The Dart has a very low power consumption and for safety includes an anti-collision sensor to ensure the desk won't pinch or trap surrounding items.

Easy to assemble, easy to keep clean, safe, and ergonomic, the Dart is an investment in your workspace and your efficiency.
